channel.title: No-ip
channel.description: ok, i am doing the no-ip route, and i got the duc, the no-ip address and everything, but my compiler isnt working. [code]@echo off title Compiler "%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause[/code] thats the code, but its not working i have java 6.1 and it worked on my other comp so, idk

item.title: No-ip
item.dc:creator: @andrew1234321 andrew1234321
item.description:
@andrew1234321 wrote:

try

@echo off
title Compiler
"%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.1_00\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java
pause

or

try

@echo off
title Compiler
"%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.1_01\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java
pause
